Package database

Class ItemOrdered

java.lang.Object
database.ItemOrdered
public class ItemOrdered extends Object
Represents an item ordered by a customer, containing details about the order item. It encapsulates the ID of the ordered item, order ID, menu item ID, and the quantity ordered.
